snippet.textDisplay:
I remember the days of having to solo him or teaming up with my little brother in MH3U against Alatreon and Dire Miralis.

We used no fkn decorations or relied on armor effects cause we saw those as senseless crutches. We just liked seeing big numbers for raw and elemental offense and defense. It was our gear with potion, mega potions, ancient potions, cool drinks, mega armor/demonskins, nullberries, and mega dashjuices and whatever the sacred land provided us, like the ballistas.

He used wither a full set of Abyssal Lagiacrus or Goldbeard Ceadeus armor with it's GS, I used a full Stygian Zinogre or Deviljho set and it's DB as we were as armor and weapon purists, and kept fighting them, and getting our asses beat.

I beat Alatreon only once and it felt like the greatest fkn ecstasy to me. I don't play anymore than casually in MHW cause I like taking it easy with abilities, mounting, mantles, decos, and other crutches for relaxing hunts, but just for Alatreon, I'm gonna cast that aside again to prep up for hunting him.

snippet.textDisplay:
Let me tell you a story of a dragon that kills not for food but for the hunt. Alatreon. A black dragon. If not, THE black dragon to survive the worst hunters across this hellish world. A beast so untameable and cunning that not even dalamadur would dare seek to tussle with this creature that is an unholy matrimony of elements.

Alatreon hath rarely been sighted in the old world and if one were to see that jet black flesh, one should hide and pray to every god and demon that the alatreon has arrived from a hunt with its bloodlust sated. This demonic dragon of the old world is capable of utilizing two forms. A first form that controls fire and dragon energy. And a second that controls ice and electric power. Switching in the blink of an eye, using all four in tandem, it is a demon that will cause ecological disasters to occur by simply existing.

Volcanoes would cool and turn to rock. Glaciers would melt. Thunderstorms would occur every blessed day. And the forests would all burn. The only hope exists in the ruiner nergigante. And even then, if the ruiner falls, all will have to leave the new world. For this, is alatreon’s world now.
